HEADWORD: Blonde
<hw>Blonde</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F., fair, light, of uncertain origin; cf. AS.
<ets>blonden-feax</ets> gray-haired, old, prop. blended-haired, as a
mixture of white and brown or black. See <er>Blend</er>, <pos>v.
