==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Blonde
<hw>Blonde</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A person of very fair complexion, with light hair and
light blue eyes.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>blond</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[So called from its color.]</ety> <def>A kind of
silk lace originally of the color of raw silk, now sometimes dyed; --
called also <altname>blond lace</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blond metal</ent>⟦br⟧
